title: Girls cross country rankings for Oct. 12, 2015
text:
Lexee Willey and her Phillipsburg teammates are ranked No. 6 this week. (Brad Wilson | For lehighvalleylive.com) By Brad Wilson | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 12, 2015 1:32 PM, updated October 12, 2015 5:37 PM View/Post Comments 
No changes this week. The first of the big postseason meets comes Thursday when Phillipsburg hosts the Hunterdon/Warren/Sussex championship at the Phillipsburg Athletic Complex, and that could well result in a shakeup. Easton looked extremely impressive in a dual meet win on that course Saturday; comparison of times will be interesting. 
1. Easton
